{"tid":1158578,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔獸世界》經典伺服器將於 8 月 27 日推出","createTime":"2019-05-17T05:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T09:03:49.000Z","uid":10751,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8bea37bd383f3b8642d92b9d4d4e6e6efa091451","tid":1158578,"uid":10751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:29:00.000Z","msg":"在日曆上做好記號：《魔獸世界》經典伺服器將於 8 月 27 日於世界各地推出！不管你的戰吼是「為了部落！」還是「為了聯盟！」，在廣闊的卡林多大陸與東部王國都有數不盡的冒險等著你。<br />\n<br />\n下表是你可以登入並體驗原汁原味的《魔獸世界》之確切日期與時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣 (CST)    6:00 a.m.    8 月 27 日</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創建你的角色<br />\n<br />\n如果你很急著要在《魔獸世界》經典伺服器中搶到你的角色名稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">注意了：我們將在 8 月 13 日星期二開放讓玩家們創建角色。</span>**遊戲帳號內有遊戲剩餘天數或遊戲剩餘時數的玩家可以在每個《魔獸世界》帳號內創建最多三個角色。我們將於日後發布更多關於伺服器名稱的訊息，不過請放心──你一定會有相當充裕的時間擬定計畫來征服你所在的伺服器！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://worldofwarcraft.com/zh-tw/news/22990080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworldofwarcraft.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnews%2F22990080&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXwVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=1fa0772f\" target=\"_blank\">https://worldofwarcraft.com/zh-tw/news/22990080</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">For the Alliance!</span></span>"},{"pid":"86afdd963653d2da3008f08d4f761ad354a2e133","tid":1158578,"uid":10751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ddce73573c334e93d8fdae9acecf561584bbda","tid":1158578,"uid":77355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"為了聯盟！"},{"pid":"448a895390bac4efddfb57bb7d043072786d7da0","tid":1158578,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"台服會有幾多人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想玩美服"}]}